==Daily==
===Searching for signal...===
{{Messages|text=
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Searching for signal...
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Unstable Signal
:'''Hyacine:''' Grayie!
:'''Hyacine:''' I'm guessing you're probably surprised to see my message, aren't you~
:'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Hyacine 02.png|80px]]
:'''Hyacine:''' Thinking about how the sky is so far away from here, I decided to prepare this little something for you in advance
:'''Hyacine:''' If you ever find yourself feeling down, remember to grab one of the snacks I packed
:'''Hyacine:''' (I really hope they're not all gone. There should be enough!)
:'''Hyacine:''' If you're not sleeping well, brew a cup of the tea I blended, and it'll knock you out before you can count five fluffy sheep
:'''Hyacine:''' Feeling stressed? Try rubbing your cheeks. They're just as soft as Little Ica's tumtum
:'''Hyacine:''' And most importantly, whatever happens, you're only allowed to be sad for a little while~
:'''Hyacine:''' Smile more! It's good for your health!
:'''Hyacine:''' ↓ Like this ↓
:'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Hyacine 04.png|80px]]
:'''Hyacine:''' When we reach the new world, may we be able to meet with a smile~
:{Choice} Hyacine, we've done it
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Hyacine, we've done it
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You've become the sky of Okhema
:{Choice} When can we meet again?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' When can we meet again?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Are you and Little Ica doing okay...?
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Message failed to send.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} The user you're trying to reach is currently out of the service area. Please try again later.
}}
