===Grayie!===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Hyacine:''' Grayie!
:'''Hyacine:''' Grayie, Grayie, Grayie, Grayie, Grayie
:{Choice} What happened?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What happened?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 16.png|80px]]
:{Choice} Cinny, Cinny, Cinny, Cinny
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Cinny, Cinny, Cinny, Cinny
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What happened?
:'''Hyacine:''' It's nothing! Little Ica just crawled over my leg and hit my shortcut keys
:'''Hyacine:''' But I did intend to find you~ After all, the decisive battle won't be a walk in the park
:'''Hyacine:''' Are your injuries getting better? Have you been sleeping well? How's your appetite? Do you feel tired at work? Any other discomfort?
:{Choice} Everything's great!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm doing great!
::'''Hyacine:''' That puts my mind at ease!
:{Choice} I love sleeping and eating, but not so much exercising
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I love sleeping and eating, but not so much exercising... Is there any hope for me, Miss Hyacine?
::'''Hyacine:''' If your body wants to sleep, let it get some rest~ You must be exhausted, so don't force yourself to stay up
::'''Hyacine:''' If you want something both healthy and delicious, well, there's another way
::'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Hyacine 01.png|80px]]
:{Choice} Is there a cure for a lack of motivation to work?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' How do you cure a lack of motivation to work?
::'''Hyacine:''' Too much stress? Easy-peasy~
::'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Hyacine 01.png|80px]]
:'''Hyacine:''' Come to the Twilight Courtyard! I'll make you some snacks~
:'''Hyacine:''' We can still bask in the sunlight, feel the breeze, and count how many times the wind chimes ring
:'''Hyacine:''' Light another one of my exclusive Twilight Herb Incense
:'''Hyacine:''' Then lie down in the cozy rocking chair and enjoy Little Ica's lullaby service
:{Choice} I'll be right there!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'll be right there!
::'''Hyacine:''' Alright, Little Ica and I will be waiting for you
:{Choice} Miracle healing!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Miracle healing!
:'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Hyacine 02.png|80px]]
}}
