===Grayie, I saw such...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Hyacine:''' Grayie, I saw such a beautiful little bird! Let me take a photostone picture to show you
:'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Message Hyacine 52.png|256px]]
:{Choice} This little bird is fed so well!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' This little bird is fed so well! Let me pet it
:{Choice} Where did this bird come from!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What's this chonky little bird doing here? Hand it over, and I'll take care of it
:'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 21 Mem 02.png|80px]]
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Hyacine has gone offline
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Hyacine has come online
:'''Hyacine:''' It was Little Ica who ran in front of the photostone! I'm holding it now
:'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Message Hyacine 53.png|256px]]
:'''Hyacine:''' Ah, the bird flew away! I almost got the shot!
:'''Hyacine:''' Its feathers are deep blue. From afar it looks like it's glowing! It's absolutely gorgeous
:'''Hyacine:''' When it just skimmed across the water, it was like a gentle flash of lightning, with splashes rising like stars
:'''Hyacine:''' Such a shame I couldn't share it with you
:{Choice} The sky was beautiful too
::'''(Trailblazer):''' But I saw the sky, and it was beautiful too
::'''Hyacine:''' Grayie is still so kind
:{Choice} I can totally see it now
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I can totally see it now. Your description really paints a picture!
::'''Hyacine:''' Grayie is still so kind
:{Choice} Let Little Ica show you what it can do
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Let Little Ica show you its gentle lightning!
::'''Hyacine:''' Haha, how did you know it's getting restless again?
:'''Hyacine:''' Next time when you return to Amphoreus, let's go together again
:'''Hyacine:''' Capture with your own eyes, and don't miss a single bird or any scenery
:{Choice} It's a promise!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You got it! It's a promise!
:{Choice} I'll be there for Hyacine!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'll be there for Hyacine!
:{Choice} To Robin's concert!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Let's go to Miss Robin's concert together!
:'''Hyacine:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Hyacine 04.png|80px]]
}}
